  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/instapaper-ios-kindle-and-airplay-support/\"><img alt=\"Instapaper AirPlay support\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/43100680b3386e946fb5b4398c6c041c/instapaper-airplay.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 465px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/instapaper\">Instapaper</a> 的设备适用范围在今天又变大了一些。在其最新的 iOS 版更新中，加入了将文章发送至 Kindle 产品阅读的功能，同时用户还可通过 AirPlay 将视频传到电视上观看。除此之外，应用中还新增了自动更新 Instapaper 订阅的选项。可能有人会觉得这次升级的内容不够给力，别急，开发团队已经透露接下来的更新将会是自被 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/04/26/betaworks-acquires-instapaper-promises-continued-development/\">Betaworks</a> 收购以来最重大的一次。那既然人家都这么说了，各位就耐心等等吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/27/instapaper-ios-kindle-and-airplay-support/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/apps/2014/02/27/instapaper-ios-now-lets-send-articles-kindle-stream-videos-via-airplay/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+TheNextWeb+%28The+Next+Web+All+Stories%29#%21xJzho\" target=\"_blank\">The Next Web</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/instapaper/id288545208?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blog.instapaper.com/post/78011513031\" target=\"_blank\">Instapaper Blog</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/instapaper-ios-kindle-and-airplay-support/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20839968/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/instapaper-ios-kindle-a